# imp1 ingestion

Entry point: `playground/imp1/ingest.py` → `parse_pdfs.run_ingestion()`.

## Config (`config.py`)

- `PDF_DIR` → `data/pdfs/`, `OUTPUT_DIR` → `output/parsed/`
- `PIPELINE_USE_OCR`, `PIPELINE_IMAGES_SCALE`, `SECTION_LABEL_MAP`

## Outputs per paper

`chunks.jsonl` (RAG input), `document.md`, `tables.json`, `formulas.json`, `pictures.json`, `document.json`, `artifacts/{pages,pictures,tables}/`.

## chunks.jsonl schema

Each line: `doc_id`, `source_file`, `title`, `authors`, `doi`, `chunk_type` (`text`|`table`|`formula`|`figure`), `section`, `text`, plus type-specific fields.

## Pipeline notes

- OCR chain: EasyOCR → RapidOCR → Tesseract → OcrAuto (`parse_pdfs._ocr_options`).
- Fresh `DocumentConverter` per PDF (see `docling-medical-a1.py`).
- Do **not** suppress `logging.getLogger("docling")` — long converts look stuck without it.
